{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762376645,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"id":"prt_ed9504348001iQ5oVvdMYhZVPr","messageID":"msg_ed95006e8001IjyvlKgzte16IY","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","type":"text","text":"Scope is bounded to the provided lineage artifact directory. I’ll load the deep-review contract, bind `artifact_dir` directly to the override, then run the single review iteration and synthesis with outputs only under that directory.","time":{"start":1781762376520,"end":1781762376644},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0ca6400b752c38e1016a3389487ae48191a4ccd9573c5c8f8b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781762388552,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_HOAP7TcDo31yKEMwPwNJagGE","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage. Read .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with spec_folder .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/A-search-retrieval, artifact dir review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-a-5, session_id fanout-gpt55r2-a-5-1781761314338-6u1ztm, executor cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast, loop_type review, maxIterations 1. Do not run resolveArtifactRoot; bind artifact_dir directly; do not touch paths outside artifact_dir; output FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55r2-a-5.","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/A-search-retrieval","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55r2-a-5-1781761314338-6u1ztm","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-a-5-1781761314338-6u1ztm\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-a-5-1781761314338-6u1ztm\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55r2-a-5-1781761314338-6u1ztm\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 227,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781762383875,"end":1781762388550}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0ca6400b752c38e1016a3389489e748191b3448c2f5bd9c857"}},"id":"prt_ed95043c6001g3Cv2uzX6LqE4G","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","messageID":"msg_ed95006e8001IjyvlKgzte16IY"}}
