{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762413010,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"id":"prt_ed950d173001giS75hXEumXs81","messageID":"msg_ed950a48e001L0oGwuxponq94A","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","type":"text","text":"User specified skill route: `deep-review`. The workflow contract allows command-driven fan-out, requires state files plus iteration markdown/JSONL delta, and forbids sub-agent dispatch; I’ll run this lineage locally rather than invoking nested agents.","time":{"start":1781762412915,"end":1781762413009},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0553a476d393bad2016a33896ce2848191a9581298b70660a1","phase":"commentary"}}}}
