{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762556161,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"id":"prt_ed952dcde001vdRs1M90gg5x89","messageID":"msg_ed952b3c2001e5miYSG5gKJQ3T","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","type":"text","text":"A stronger handler/cache defect is emerging: ranking-affecting `folderBoost` is applied after pipeline formatting, but the cache key does not include it. I’m confirming the internal callers and cache write path before recording it.","time":{"start":1781762546910,"end":1781762556158},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_09ac95a715e75c53016a3389f2e0c08191b898790e8364a1ad","phase":"commentary"}}}}
