{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762627562,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"id":"prt_ed95407040018vYNmyq2HBAxQ2","messageID":"msg_ed9538e44001Hvdwu31upVSbQK","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","type":"text","text":"I’m verifying the schema’s `getSchema` behavior so the `retrievalLevel` finding is not based only on absence from one list.","time":{"start":1781762623236,"end":1781762627561},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0a1e58f7b3e27324016a338a3f2a5c8191bc1cb6681ace5100","phase":"commentary"}}}}
