{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763466105,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"id":"prt_ed960e316001uOA2fnDOBmEvkc","messageID":"msg_ed960bd78001isNzamocN7aLuv","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","type":"text","text":"The contract has one mismatch with the fan-out instruction: normal deep-review says to use `resolveArtifactRoot`, while the prior user constraint explicitly overrode that and bound the lineage directory directly. I’m preserving the explicit override and only validating files under that directory.","time":{"start":1781763466006,"end":1781763466105},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_05a76eef3d526026016a338d89f87081919d928a69a4599544","phase":"commentary"}}}}
