{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763573331,"sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","part":{"id":"prt_ed9628167001KssbUPv5Npigv5","messageID":"msg_ed9624647001fQTlUSSv0S04Dn","sessionID":"ses_126affd45ffeTNBTsc65PNhoaD","type":"text","text":"One artifact can be improved inside the allowed lineage directory: `deltas/iteration-001.json` has finding refs and counts but not the full `findingDetails[]` payload that the deep-review quality gate expects. I’m adding the existing registry-backed finding detail objects there, without touching the review target or scope folder.","time":{"start":1781763572071,"end":1781763573328},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_00b87b2e0cc442bf016a338df409f08191be971b702b5aa174","phase":"commentary"}}}}
